{
  "text": "Our third research question concerned sex differences. We hypothesized that females will endorse the performance-avoidance goals more than males. Although, Elliot's [CITATION_1] original theories only extended to performance-avoidance goals, we also tested his hypothesis with the mastery-avoidance goal.",
